race.comment: GREATESTOFEASE (5) backs up quickly after chasing strongly into the frame two days ago at Murray Bridge. Can take closer order from the kinder draw and doesn't need to improve much to get the verdict. GOGOLF GURU (11) is ticking along nicely, placing in her last five but is just lacking the winning blow. Should blend into the race nicely again and can get the job done. DIDWEWIN (4) didn't give her rivals a sniff on Christmas Eve when leading pillar-to-post here. With similar tactics she can make it two on the bounce. BLACK BUGATTI (2) got too far back last time on the Parks track but if she can be closer when turning this time, she's a genuine threat. LADY SKYLLA (10) continues to leave herself with too much to do but does get a key booking in Milnes from a good draw. Can improve sharply.
